snippet.textDisplay:
Just two days back,I got introduced to this wonderful rendition by Ms Sona and it has left such an effect on my heart and soul that I've been listening to it over and over again,losing counts of it.It has led me to search for her other renditions.
                        Who cares,if it doesn't confirm to the traditions.All I know,I've fallen in love again and this time with life !
                   'Sona ,Aap sach much SONA hain'

                 Ye hee hain hamari duayen
                 Aap hazzarron sal jeeyen.
                 Lakhon ganen aise nikle,Aap ke juban se
                 Jees par korodo jhumein,hum jaise
